		<div id="siteNotice"><script type='text/javascript'>if (wgNotice != '') document.writeln(wgNotice);</script></div>		<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading">Sun Tzu</h1>
		<div id="bodyContent">
			<h3 id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</h3>
			<div id="contentSub"></div>
									<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->
			<div class="dablink">This article is about the military strategist.  For the mathematician, see <a href="/wiki/Sun_Tzu_(mathematician)" title="Sun Tzu (mathematician)">Sun Tzu (mathematician)</a>.</div>
<table class="infobox vcard vevent" style="width:22em; font-size:90%; text-align:left;">
<tr>
<th colspan="2" style="text-align:center; font-size:larger;" class="fn summary">Sun Tzu</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" style="text-align:center;" class=""><a href="/wiki/File:Enchoen27n3200.jpg" class="image" title="Enchoen27n3200.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/37/Enchoen27n3200.jpg/200px-Enchoen27n3200.jpg" width="200" height="301" border="0" /></a><br />
<small>Statue of Sun Tzu in <a href="/wiki/Yurihama,_Tottori" title="Yurihama, Tottori">Yurihama, Tottori</a>, <a href="/wiki/Japan" title="Japan">Japan</a></small></td>
</tr>
